         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Stategarden, Melbourne, ¶ Easterday 1867. ¶ Sir, ¶  ¶ Dr. Jas. C. Cox, M.D., of Sydney, Author of a scientific enumeration of Australian Land-and Freshwater Shells ¶  and now engaged on an illustrated...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">67.04.21c</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To George Bentham</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Linnean Society, London, Certificates of Fellows, Foreign Members and Associates 1865-1870.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Stategarden, Melbourne,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Easterday 1867.<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">In 1867, Easter fell on 21 April.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Dr. Jas. C. Cox, M.D., of Sydney, Author of a scientific enumeration of Australian Land-and Freshwater Shells<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Cox (1864).</p>
               </note> and now engaged on an illustrated work on the same branch of science,<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Cox (1868).</p>
               </note> is desirous of becoming a fellow of the L.S., and I feel thus much pleasure to be his sponsor for recommending that Gentleman to that honor, as I am certain that he will prove a useful and valuable member.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Very obediently</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. Mueller<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">The MS has also been signed by G. Bentham and J. Hooker and it thus became the formal nomination certificate.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">G. Bentham Esq.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">P L.S. <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>F.R.S. &amp;c &amp;c<note xml:id="ftn5" type="footnote" n="5">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Annotated at foot of front of sheet:</seg> Proposed Novr 7th 1867 | Ballot Jany 16th 1868. <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <hi rend="underline">Elected</hi>
                     </seg> Rd. K.</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">On back of sheet</seg>: Jas. C. Cox | Elected Jany 16th 1868 | Bentham. </p>
               </note>
            </p>
